    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The recurrent neural network (RNN) layer initialized with a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnnsinglegatedescriptor",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " transforms the input data (image or matrix) and previous output with a set of filters. Each produces one feature map in the new output data. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You may provide the RNN unit with a single input or a sequence of inputs.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2888084",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Description of Operation",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x_j",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the input data (at time index ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "t",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " of sequence, ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "j",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " index containing quadruplet: batch index, ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x,y",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and feature index (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x = y = 0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " for matrices)).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "h0_j",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the recurrent input (previous output) data from previous time step (at time index ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "t-1",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " of sequence).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "h1_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the output data produced at this time step.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "W_ij, U_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the weights for input and recurrent input data, respectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "b_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be a bias term.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "gi(x)",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be a neuron activation function.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The new output image ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "h1_i",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " data is computed as follows:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "h1_i = gi( W_ij * x_j + U_ij * h0_j  + b_i )"
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2888085",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          },
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "*",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " stands for convolution (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnnimageinferencelayer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") or matrix-vector/matrix multiplication (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnnmatrixinferencelayer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ").",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Summation is over index ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "j",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (except for the batch index), but there's no summation over repeated index ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "i",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (the output index).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Note that for validity, all intermediate images must be of same size, and the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "U",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " matrix must be square (that is, ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnndescriptor/2865702-outputfeaturechannels",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "==",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnndescriptor/2865707-inputfeaturechannels",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "). Also, the bias terms are scalars with regard to spatial dimensions.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
